Tom Pierce, CA - Chief Financial Officer
As CFO of the Clarity group of companies, Tom is responsible for providing the overall financial oversight to companies in which Clarity invests. In addition to a varied corporate finance, CFO, controller and treasury skill set, Tom brings investor relations, corporate planning and IPO experience. He has been active in the resource sector since 1992, in Canadian and Mexican operations. He was previously CFO of Grande Cache Coal Corporation, Canada's second largest metallurgical coal producer, where he lead the successful IPO and the investor relations program.
